{"type":"message","id":"8b776560","parentId":"50baa981","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:04:26.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The **youtube-research** skill is ready.\n\n**What it does:**\n\n• **Search YouTube** - Find videos by topic, sorted by relevance, date, or views\n\n• **Get video details** - Title, duration, views, likes, comments, resolution, captions status, tags\n\n• **Extract transcripts** - Auto-generated or manual captions from videos\n\n• **Summarize content** - Use AI to summarize transcripts after extraction\n\n---\n\n**Files created:**\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `youtube-research.skill` | Packaged skill file (in workspace) |\n| `scripts/youtube_search.py` | Main Python script |\n| `references/advanced.md` | Advanced usage patterns |\n\n---\n\n**To install yt-dlp** (required for transcripts):\n\n```bash\nsudo apt install yt-dlp\n# or\npip install yt-dlp\n```\n\n---\n\n**Example usage:**\n\n```bash\n# Search\npython scripts/youtube_search.py --search \"python async\" --max 5\n\n# Details\npython scripts/youtube_search.py --video VIDEO_ID --details\n\n# Transcript\npython scripts/youtube_search.py --video VIDEO_ID --transcript\n\n# Full analysis\npython scripts/youtube_search.py --video VIDEO_ID --full\n```\n\nThe skill is packaged at `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/youtube-research.skill` and ready to use."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":31026,"output":289,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31315,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774793007810,"responseId":"chatcmpl-82084b9816a5acc6"}}
