{"type":"message","id":"b90b96a9","parentId":"291328b6","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:09:40.020Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-83350cfacecc53b7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 5 INSANE OpenClaw Use Cases (New Superpowers)\n**URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O-01egh0vvs\n**Channel:** Jack Roberts\n**Published:** 2026-03-26\n**Duration:** 15:57\n\n## Statistics\n- Views: 12,833\n- Likes: 267\n- Comments: 34\n\n## Technical Details\n- Definition: HD\n- Dimension: 2d\n- Projection: rectangular\n- Has Captions: No\n- Licensed Content: Yes\n\n## Description\n📈 ALL Systems: https://bit.ly/4kol0y5\n🎁 FREE Resources: https://bit.ly/40y9bfI\n🎙️ AI Notepad: https://granola.so/\n\n\nOpenClaw is one of the most powerful software on the planet, and when you use it correctly, you can unlock superpowers that give you so much productivity and can accelerate your business. In this video, I show five incredible use cases that you can unlock immediately. \n\nCORE Software\n📊 token costs: https://cost-optimizer-ten.vercel.app\n🚀 AntiGravity: https://antigravity.google/\n🦞 OpenClaw: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw\n🌲 Pinecone: https://www.pinecone.io/\n🔥 n8n: https://n8n.partnerlinks.io/rkk4h07a86pv\n💬 ChatGPT: https://chatgpt.com/\n♊ Gemini: https://gemini.google.com/\n☁️ Claude: https://claude.ai/\n📝 NotebookLM: https://notebooklm.google.com/\n🎙️ My Goofy pod: https://bit.ly/46nLQ3U"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":376,"aggregated":"# 5 INSANE OpenClaw Use Cases (New Superpowers)\n**URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O-01egh0vvs\n**Channel:** Jack Roberts\n**Published:** 2026-03-26\n**Duration:** 15:57\n\n## Statistics\n- Views: 12,833\n- Likes: 267\n- Comments: 34\n\n## Technical Details\n- Definition: HD\n- Dimension: 2d\n- Projection: rectangular\n- Has Captions: No\n- Licensed Content: Yes\n\n## Description\n📈 ALL Systems: https://bit.ly/4kol0y5\n🎁 FREE Resources: https://bit.ly/40y9bfI\n🎙️