{"type":"message","id":"75df334a","parentId":"10696fa4","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:10:10.052Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The video doesn't have captions available (auto-generated or manual), so I can't extract a transcript. This is a limitation - some videos don't have any captions.\n\n**What I can tell you:**\n\n| | |\n|--|--|\n| **Title** | 5 INSANE OpenClaw Use Cases (New Superpowers) |\n| **Channel** | Jack Roberts |\n| **Duration** | 15:57 |\n| **Published** | 2026-03-26 |\n| **Views** | 12,833 |\n\n**Description summary:** The video covers 5 powerful OpenClaw use cases that unlock \"superpowers\" for productivity and business acceleration.\n\n**To get the transcript:**\n- The video has no captions available\n- You could ask the creator to add captions\n- Or watch and I can help you take notes\n\nWould you like me to search for similar OpenClaw videos that might have transcripts available?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":32579,"output":192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774793394351,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9954ccdab299a683"}}
