{"type":"message","id":"0cb3b020","parentId":"0a939a89","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:56:53.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It works! Let me now update the skill documentation and re-package:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-aa0136f90674c4c8","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"/home/ivo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/youtube-research/SKILL.md","newText":"## Requirements\n\n- `YOUTUBE_KEY` in `.env` file (YouTube Data API v3 key)\n- Python 3.6+ (standard library only for basic usage)\n- For transcripts (automatic fallback chain):\n  1. `youtube-transcript-api` - works from personal machines: `pip install youtube-transcript-api`\n  2. `faster-whisper` + `yt-dlp` - works from VPS/cloud: `pip install faster-whisper yt-dlp`\n\n**Note:** Search and video details work without any additional packages.","oldText":"## Requirements\n\n- `YOUTUBE_KEY` in `.env` file (YouTube Data API v3 key)\n- Python 3.6+ (standard library only for basic usage)\n- `youtube-transcript-api` for transcript extraction: `pip install youtube-transcript-api`\n\n**Note:** Search and video details work without any additional packages. Transcript extraction requires `youtube-transcript-api`."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":56670,"output":252,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56922,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774796175696,"responseId":"chatcmpl-81276a1dad402fb4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9fab89d","parentId":"0cb3b020","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:56:54.028Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-aa0136f90674c4c8","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ivo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/youtube-research/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  26 ## Requirements\n  27 \n  28 - `YOUTUBE_KEY` in `.env` file (YouTube Data API v3 key)\n  29 - Python 3.6+ (standard library only for basic usage)\n- 30 - `youtube-transcript-api` for transcript extraction: `pip install youtube-transcript-api`\n+ 30 - For transcripts (automatic fallback chain):\n+ 31   1. `youtube-transcript-api` - works from personal machines: `pip install youtube-transcript-api`\n+ 32   2. `faster-whisper` + `yt-dlp` - works from VPS/cloud: `pip install faster-whisper yt-dlp`\n  31 \n- 32 **Note:** Search and video details work without any additional packages. Transcript extraction requires `youtube-transcript-api`.\n+ 34 **Note:** Search and video details work without any additional packages.\n  33 \n  34 ## Core Workflows\n  35 \n  36 ### 1. Search Videos\n     ...","firstChangedLine":30},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774796214025}}
{"type":"message","id":"885e6984","parentId":"a9fab89d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:57:43.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-8dc437e281c4ccd2","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"/home/ivo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/youtube-research/SKILL.md","newText":"## Limitations\n\n- Transcript extraction depends on YouTube's caption availability\n- Auto-generated captions may have errors\n- Some videos have no captions available\n- **IP blocking**: YouTube blocks `youtube-transcript-api` from cloud/VPS IPs\n  - Fallback: Uses local Whisper transcription (downloads audio, transcribes)\n\n### How Transcript Extraction Works\n\n1. **First**: Try `youtube-transcript-api` (fast, works from personal machines)\n2. **Fallback**: Download audio + transcribe with `faster-whisper` (works from VPS/cloud)\n\nThe fallback is automatic - you don't need to do anything.","oldText":"## Limitations\n\n- Transcript extraction depends on YouTube's caption availability\n- Auto-generated captions may have errors\n- Some videos have no captions available\n- **IP blocking**: YouTube blocks requests from cloud providers (AWS, GCP, Azure, etc.)\n  - Works from personal machines (laptops, desktops)\n  - May fail from VPS/servers\n\n### When Transcript Fails\n\nIf running from a server/VPS:\n\n```bash\n# Use yt-dlp instead (may also be blocked)\nyt-dlp --write-auto-sub --sub-lang en --skip-download \"URL\"\n\n# Or download video and use local Whisper\nyt-dlp -o video.mp4 \"URL\"\nwhisper video.mp4\n```"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":56965,"output":318,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774796214031,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bc168c0ee20ca33e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"94249add","parentId":"885e6984","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:57:43.858Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-8dc437e281c4ccd2","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/ivo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/youtube-research/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 130 \n 131 - Transcript extraction depends on YouTube's caption availability\n 132 - Auto-generated captions may have errors\n 133 - Some videos have no captions available\n-134 - **IP blocking**: YouTube blocks requests from cloud providers (AWS, GCP, Azure, etc.)\n-135   - Works from personal machines (laptops, desktops)\n-136   - May fail from VPS/servers\n+134 - **IP blocking**: YouTube blocks `youtube-transcript-api` from cloud/VPS IPs\n+135   - Fallback: Uses local Whisper transcription (downloads audio, transcribes)\n 137 \n-138 ### When Transcript Fails\n+137 ### How Transcript Extraction Works\n 139 \n-140 If running from a server/VPS:\n+139 1. **First**: Try `youtube-transcript-api` (fast, works from personal machines)\n+140 2. **Fallback**: Download audio + transcribe with `faster-whisper` (works from VPS/cloud)\n 141 \n-142 ```bash\n-143 # Use yt-dlp instead (may also be blocked)\n-144 yt-dlp --write-auto-sub --sub-lang en --skip-download \"URL\"\n+142 The fallback is automatic - you don't need to do anything.\n 145 \n-146 # Or download video and use local Whisper\n-147 yt-dlp -o video.mp4 \"URL\"\n-148 whisper video.mp4\n-149 ```\n-150 \n 151 ## Advanced Usage\n 152 \n 153 See [references/advanced.md](references/advanced.md) for:\n 154 - Search query optimization\n     ...","firstChangedLine":134},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774796263854}}
