{"type":"message","id":"ec171071","parentId":"bbb773f6","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:58:08.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me summarize the video for you:\n\n---\n\n# Key Points: \"5 INSANE OpenClaw Use Cases\"\n\n**1. Expand Your Universe - Skills Integration**\n- Connect Claude Code skills directly to OpenClaw\n- Access any skill from your phone via Telegram bot\n- No need to duplicate skills across platforms\n- Example: Bitly link shortening works from Telegram chat\n\n**2. Meeting & System Intelligence - Granola Integration**\n- Connect Granola (AI notepad) via MCP to OpenClaw\n- Captures meeting transcripts + your private notes\n- Auto-generates action items\n- Can add tasks to your task board automatically\n\n**3. Multi-Expert Debates**\n- Spin up multiple AI experts on different models\n- Have them debate topics from different perspectives\n- Save outputs as HTML documents\n- Example: Three experts debating which country to live in (tax, lifestyle, contrarian views)\n\n**4. Overnight Agents**\n- Schedule recurring tasks that run while you sleep\n- Use free models (DeepSeek) to save costs\n- Example: Daily report with one actionable improvement suggestion based on your context\n\n**5. The Negotiator - Agent Deployment**\n- Identify areas where agents can negotiate/research for you\n- Examples: Find 20 sponsorship prospects, research Asian expansion markets\n- Integrate with Gmail (draft-only for safety)\n- Creates execution logs and strategies\n\n**Key Themes:**\n- Context engineering is the biggest trend\n- Co-pilot vs System distinction\n- Having a command center/dashboard to visualize AI activity\n- Security: Restrict email to draft-only, keep human in the loop\n\n---\n\nThe skill is now fully working! It automatically falls back to Whisper transcription when YouTube blocks the IP."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":57502,"output":356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0